RHPAM git import is not backward compatible We need to support a range of versions for backward compatibility

We are going to support:
* A filtered resource that will replace take the list of valid versions from kie-parent pom.xml
* An environment variable that will contain a comma-separated list of supported versions. Those versions will be appended to list declared in kie-parent pom.xml


h2. Example:
{code:xml}
<org.kie.validation.dependency.versions>
7.0.1-redhat-8,7.0.2-redhat-10
</org.kie.validation.dependency.version>
{code}

{code:bash}
*-Dorg.kie.validation.dependency.versions=7.0.1-redhat-8,7.0.2-redhat-10*
{code}

